    end
  end

  # ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
  # assert_has_keys/2
  # ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

  @doc """
  Asserts that `map` contains every key in `keys`.

  `keys` may be a list of keys or a single bare key. On failure the message
